JavaScript Fu Rails Plugin
==========================


Extended JavaScript Tasks
-------------------------
  rake statistics
includes files in public/javascripts

  rake notes
includes files in public/javascripts


'Calls JavaScript' RSpec Matcher
--------------------------------
Use these in your specs:
  response.should call_js('fn')
  response.should call_js('fn(true)')
  response.should call_js('gApp.setup')


